\title{AI-Powered Security System for Real-Time Detection of Cyber Threats}

\author{John Smith}

\date{\today}

\maketitle

\section{Introduction}

With the increasing prevalence of cyber attacks, it has become essential for organizations to have a robust security system that can detect and block potential threats in real-time. Traditional security systems are no longer sufficient, as cyber criminals are constantly developing new attack techniques that can easily bypass them. Therefore, an AI-powered security system is required that can adapt to these new threats and provide comprehensive protection to enterprise applications.

\section{AI-Powered Security System}

The proposed AI-powered security system utilizes machine learning algorithms that can identify and block potential cyber threats in real-time. These algorithms are capable of self-adapting to new attack techniques, ensuring that the security system remains effective even against the latest threats.

Furthermore, the security system provides granular access control to all users, ensuring that only authorized personnel can access sensitive data. All data transmissions within the enterprise application are monitored and logged, allowing for easy identification of any suspicious activities.

\section{User Activity Monitoring}

The security system also provides complete audit logs of all user activities, allowing for easy identification of any unauthorized access or suspicious activities. This feature is essential for compliance with regulations such as GDPR and HIPAA, as it provides a comprehensive record of all user activities.

\section{Contingency Plans}

In the event of a security breach, the system has contingency plans in place to handle the situation. These plans include isolating affected systems, blocking access to sensitive data, and notifying relevant personnel.

\section{Conclusion}

An AI-powered security system is essential for any organization that wants to protect its enterprise applications from cyber threats. With its ability to adapt to new attack techniques, provide granular access control, and monitor all user activities, this system provides comprehensive protection to sensitive data. Furthermore, its contingency plans ensure that any security breaches are handled effectively and efficiently.

\end{document}

